DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

96-2808. Cuyahoga Cty. Bar Assn. v. Boychuk.

On August 22, 1997, respondent filed an affidavit of compliance. Whereas the affidavit of compliance did not contain a proof of service as required by S.Ct.Prac.R. XIV(2),

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that respondent’s affidavit of compliance be, and hereby is, stricken.
